query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS leads (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  leadNumber VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  leadType ENUM('affiliate', 'partnership', 'distributor', 'wholesale', 'retail') NOT NULL,
  leadStatus ENUM('new', 'contacted', 'qualified', 'negotiating', 'won', 'lost') DEFAULT 'new',
  firstName VARCHAR(255),
  lastName VARCHAR(255),
  companyName VARCHAR(500),
  email VARCHAR(320),
  phone VARCHAR(50),
  website VARCHAR(500),
  source VARCHAR(255),
  estimatedValue DECIMAL(10,2),
  expectedCloseDate TIMESTAMP,
  notes TEXT,
  assignedTo INT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  convertedAt TIMESTAMP,
  convertedToCustomerId INT,
  INDEX status_idx (leadStatus),
  INDEX type_idx (leadType),
  FOREIGN KEY (assignedTo) REFERENCES users(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (convertedToCustomerId) REFERENCES customers(id)
)
